<voice_0x01000F22><se_def>Prince Charmles: This is it! This is exactly what I needed!
This will show Father and his servants!

<voice_0x01000F23><se_def>Prince Charmles: I can just see their faces now! 'Oh, Charmles! How wonderful! What a hero you are!'
They'd better, after all I went through to get it!
<voice_0x01000F24><se_def>Prince Charmles: Servants! Back to the castle!
